reviewText: Bait of Satan Dvd, John Bevere - I have seen this before on t.v. - it was nicely made but I haven't watched dvd yet

This content is extremely valuable to practically any Christian.  John makes the subject of forgiveness very accessible.  If you have not seen, it is a must see!  This could spark a major attitude shift in Bible believing Christians, maybe even a revival that sweeps the entire western hemisphere.
I was pleased with this purchase.  It arrived on time and in proper condition. Thanks you.
